Package junittest

Class MemberListTest

java.lang.Object
junittest.MemberListTest
public class MemberListTest extends Object
The MemberListTest class is designed for testing the functionality of the MemberList class. It includes a series of test methods that verify the correct behavior of MemberList's methods under various conditions. The default constructor of this class is used implicitly by the testing framework to instantiate the test class before executing the test methods. This setup facilitates the preparation of a controlled testing environment for the MemberList functionalities.
Author:
Soham Patel

      static MemberList members
      A static reference to a MemberList object used for testing purposes. This member list is intended to be shared across all test cases within the MemberListTest class. It provides a common setup for managing a collection of Member objects that can be used to test the functionalities and methods of the MemberList class in a consistent manner.
